For unit, there will be only 6 options [For Options, use screenshot attached: '@/swipe/1.png' ]  For this, make a dropdown menu to select the units and make sure to update the schema for this



<Button
                          variant="outline"
                          size="sm"
                          onClick={() => updateQuantity(product.id, quantity - 1)}
                          disabled={disabled}
                          className="h-8 w-8 p-0"
                        >
                          <Minus className="h-3 w-3" />
                        </Button>


<Button
                          variant="outline"
                          size="sm"
                          onClick={() => updateQuantity(product.id, quantity + 1)}
                          disabled={disabled}
                          className="h-8 w-8 p-0"
                        >
                          <Plus className="h-3 w-3" />
                        </Button>